1. Hive is sql query type language to query the data which is sitting on top of hdfs.

2. Hive converts the queries into map-reduce tasks which executed on data nodes and result sent to driver once task finished.

3. It can process the various types of files such as avro, Parquet etc.

4. Hive can able to process the only the structure data.

5. Hive is not intended for row updates and deletes because hive intended for olap but not for oltp. The reason for that is it
   converts every query into map-reduce tasks which could take some time to execute.
